      • categorizeObject

        public String categorizeObject(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedObject named,
                      Map<String,String> idspaceMappings,
                      Set<String> useNamespace,
                      boolean useFallback)
        Create a category for a given named object. There are three options:
        1. use id space to lookup category string in the id space map
        2. use OBO namespace, if the is space is in useNamespace set
        3. fallback: use id space prefix (string before first colon)
        Parameters:
        named -
        idspaceMappings -
        useNamespace -
        useFallback - if false ignore fall-back
        Returns:
        category or null
